ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:
This Python implementation is based on the UTCI Fortran code (Version a 0.002, 
October 2009) originally developed under COST Action 730. The original work was 
released for public use after termination of COST Action 730.

Reference:
Bröde P, Fiala D, Błażejczyk K, Holmér I, Jendritzky G, Kampmann B, Tinz B, 
Havenith G (2012) Deriving the operational procedure for the Universal Thermal 
Climate Index (UTCI). Int J Biometeorol 56(3):481-494. 
doi:10.1007/s00484-011-0454-1